glosses: to pray for something bad to happen to someone, to maledict, to curse

examples.translation: I maledicted him after our fight

glosses: to curse, to cuss, to swear, to say a swear word

etymology: Inherited from Ottoman Turkish ایلنمك (ilenmek), from Old Anatolian Turkish ایلنمك (ilänmäk), from Proto-Turkic *ilen-
